Cell.Text: Now we have the witches' heads, so we must go to Ysgramor's Tomb, and burn them in the Harbinger Flame.
We did... Kodlak has already paid for his mistake. Now his soul may rest from its torment... | But maybe the price he paid was too high...
Now the Companions are cleaned from Hircine's curse. I think it was worth it.
Yes, I agree with you. And now the war is over. | I have one more thing to ask.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M90_ASK_Topic02: Now the Companions are cleaned from Hircine's curse. I think it was worth it.

Cell.Text: He allowed the Companions to kill Krev. He deserved it!
Yes, Krev perished as well... | But I hope Kodlak and Krev are right now on Sovngarde putting all the anger and hate aside and sharing a sweet mead mug. | I have one more thing to ask.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M90_ASK_Topic03: He allowed the Companions to kill Krev. He deserved it!

Cell.Text: I think you are right. But now we cannot go back in time...
Yes. But at least the companions are free from this ancient curse. And we are not enemies anymore. I hope our legates may rejoin again someday. | I have one more thing to ask.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M90_ASK_Topic04: I think you are right. But now we cannot go back in time...

Cell.Text: I think you should be the new Silver Hand leader. | I really think I'm better with my research than with leadership. | If wasn't for you, we wouldn't have made it. | Do you accept?
[S] Good. Hillara and Sennar are responsible for managing the contracts. | Talk to them to organize the wolf hunts. | Please, hold this axe and kill some beasts for me.
[S] Also, I would like to ask you to come back to Driftshade in some days. I'm finishing another piece of research.
I think I'm not ready for this yet...
[S] I understand. If you change your mind, come talk to me at Driftshade. | Hillara and Sennar will responsible for managing the hunt's contracts. Talk to them if you want to help.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M90_ASK_Topic08: I think I'm not ready for this yet...

Cell.Text: I decide to accept the Silver Hands' leadership.

[S] Good. I knew you were going to accept. | Talk to Hillara and Senaar to organize the wolf hunts and contracts. Also, talk to him if you want to improve your new leader's quarters. | Please, hold this ax and kill some beasts for me.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M90_DAL_Topic01: I decide to accept the Silver Hands' leadership.
